        %h4 LEE LINDEN
        %strong.job_title Co-founder and Vice President, Business Development
        %p Lee Linden is the co-founder of Tapjoy, a platform offering mobile publishers solutions for application discovery, rich advertising, and virtual good sales.
        %p Lee previously worked in product development at Microsoft, helping engineer both enterprise and consumer offerings. He also co-founded ContestMachine.com, a self-service online promotional marketing service with thousands of small business customers.
        %p Lee studied computer engineering at the University of Michigan and has an MBA from Stanford's Graduate School of Business.
