        %h4 BEN LEWIS
        %strong.job_title Co-founder and Vice President, Mobile Product
        %p Ben is the co-founder of Tapjoy, a platform offering mobile publishers solutions for application discovery, rich advertising, and virtual good sales.
        %p Ben previously worked at Google where he spent 4 years as a Product Manager working on products such as Toolbar, Checkout, and Search.  Ben has also worked at Microsoft as an engineer on the original Xbox Live team.
        %p Ben has an undergraduate degree in Computer Engineering and an MBA from the University of Michigan.
