        %h4 SHANNON JESSUP
        %strong.job_title Vice President, Sales and Marketing
        %p Shannon Jessup joined Tapjoy to lead our sales efforts with advertisers and advertising agencies. Ms. Jessup has over 15 years of leadership experience in all facets of high technology including channels, sales, marketing and operations. Jessup's expertise is building effective, revenue-generating client and partner relationships that help companies meet their business goals.
        %p Prior to Offerpal, she was the head of sales and business development for Commission Junction, a global leader in the online advertising channels of affiliate marketing and managed search. Before Commission Junction she was the director of worldwide channels for Citrix Online (CTXS), a leading provider of on-demand applications for remote access, Web conferencing and collaboration.  Ms. Jessup has also held senior level positions for companies including Epoch Internet and Merisel (MSEL).
        %p Ms. Jessup started her career with IBM as a collegiate sales representative and received her Bachelor of Arts degree in economics from the University of California Santa Barbara.  She is originally from Northern California and currently makes her home in Santa Barbara with her husband and three children.
