        %h4 NAGHI PRASAD
        %strong.job_title Vice President, Engineering and Operations
        %p Naghi Prasad has developed award-winning products for online advertising and analytics companies. Most recently, he was the Vice President of Engineering and Operations at Turn, a contextual advertising company building a next-generation automatic bidded CPA advertising network. Prior to that, Naghi was the VP of Engineering for Intelligent Content and Search at Verity, overseeing products that contributed over $100 million in annual revenues.
        %p Previously, Naghi held senior management roles at Peoplesoft and VerticalNet, leading their data warehousing and analytics initiatives and creating award-winning product suites. As a member of the Accenture technology think tank organization, he led a number of initiatives on emerging technologies including search, knowledge management and complex systems modeling. 
        %p Naghi has a Ph.D. in artificial intelligence from the University of Massachusetts, a master's degree from the Massachusetts Institute of Technology, and bachelor's and master's degrees in computer science and electrical engineering from the Indian Institute of Technology, Chennai.
