        %h4 JEN NEE TANG
        %strong.job_title Vice President, Finance
        %p Jen Nee Tang is the Vice President of Finance at Tapjoy, responsible for all finance and accounting operations. Jen has fifteen years of leadership and broad operational experience in venture-backed Internet and software companies. She started her career in public accounting with PricewaterhouseCoopers in London.
        %p Prior to Tapjoy, Jen held finance positions at venture-backed companies such as eCredit/Cortera (online credit risk management), Endeca Technologies (enterprise search), and iKena (instant messaging and web co-browsing).
        %p Jen received her Bachelor of Science degree in Accounting &amp; Financial Analysis from the University of Warwick in England and is a Chartered Accountant with the Institute of Chartered Accountants in England &amp; Wales.
